## 6. What Data We Can Collect

### Strong Coverage
- Repo inventory  
- Workflow runs  
- Audit logs  
- Git traffic (via governor)  
- Activity patterns  

References:
- https://cli.github.com/manual/  
- https://docs.github.com/en/enterprise-server@3.14/admin/monitoring-activity-in-your-enterprise  
- https://github.com/orgs/community/discussions/34220  

---

### Missing / Weak Coverage

- CPU (full system level)  
- Memory usage  
- Request latency  
- API performance  
- Service errors  

Reference:  
https://docs.github.com/en/enterprise-server@3.16/admin/monitoring-and-managing-your-instance/monitoring-your-instance/about-the-monitor-dashboards  

